data.description: Location! Location! Location! In the heart of Old Town, on a dead end street, next to Japanese Gulch, easy walk to the dog park, restaurants and the waterfront. Lower level has been remodeled with a second kitchen and has an outside entrance. Warm and cozy fireplace on the main level and wood stove in the basement. Forced air gas (propane) heat. Composition roof only a few years old. Outbuilding perfect for a shop,  studio or second garage. Mature landscaping provides lots of privacy. Main level has beautiful hardwood floors, covered porches front and rear.  Wood stove on the lower level for added comfort surrounded by River Rock. Not many homes come up for sale in this area. Seller completed inspection available upon request.
